    <h1>Scientific Publications</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="container" style="padding:40px 20px;">
    <p style="font-size:1.1rem;color:#555;margin-bottom:40px;max-width:800px;">Dr. Tal Lavian has published extensively on telecommunications, network architecture, grid computing, and advanced networking technologies. Below is a comprehensive list of his scientific publications across peer-reviewed journals, conferences, and technical venues.</p>

    <div style="border-left:4px solid #2d3e6f;padding:15px 20px;margin:20px 0;background:#f8fafc;">
      <h3 style="margin-bottom:6px;">Communications Architecture – Grid Computing</h3>
      <p style="color:#555;margin:0;">Scholar's Press, 2013</p>
    </div>

    <div style="border-left:4px solid #2d3e6f;padding:15px 20px;margin:20px 0;background:#f8fafc;">
      <h3 style="margin-bottom:6px;">R&D Models for Advanced Development</h3>
      <p style="color:#555;margin:0;">ASEE, 2015</p>
    </div>

    <div style="border-left:4px solid #2d3e6f;padding:15px 20px;margin:20px 0;background:#f8fafc;">
